<br>
As a result, I hereby declare:<br>
<br>
1.  I will never group with a d00d<br>
2.  I will never sell to a d00d<br>
3.  I will never buy from a d00d<br>
4.  I will never assist a d00d.<br>
5.  I will never heal a d00d.<br>
6.  I will never stop a d00d's train.<br>
<br>
